her your knowledge. Master alchemy, thaumaturgy and divination to construct artifacts of immense power.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/658830/extras/5a324682686073fa4ee29c354f4dc7da.poster.avif?t=1754054593\" width=578 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/658830/extras/5a324682686073fa4ee29c354f4dc7da.webm?t=1754054593\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/658830/extras/5a324682686073fa4ee29c354f4dc7da.mp4?t=1754054593\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Explore Alcor</h2><br>Steal arcane secrets from ancient ruins. Learn alien languages to read magical grimoires. Fight monsters and dissect them to learn their weaknesses. Harvest valuable alchemical ingredients.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/658830/extras/0333fff1e0194caf2b83796160e5cc77.poster.avif?t=1754054593\" width=578 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/658830/extras/0333fff1e0194caf2b83796160e5cc77.webm?t=1754054593\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/658830/extras/0333fff1e0194caf2b83796160e5cc77.mp4?t=1754054593\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
